ney">Disney+</a>上观看。</p><p>金· <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/american-horror-story-delicate-trailer-debuts-kim-kardashian-3471781">卡戴珊 (Kim Kardashian) 在令人毛骨悚然的“美国恐怖故事：精致”预告片中首次亮相，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
